import React from 'react'

function Header() {
  return (
    <>
    
       <Navbar>
         <Navbar.Brand>My Portfolio</Navbar.Brand>
         <Navigator.Toogle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav"/>
         <Navbar.Collapse>
            <Nav className="ml-auto">
                <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
         </Navbar.Collapse>
       </Navbar>
    
    </>
  )
}

export default Header
